CONCEPT: ASYMMETRY
M 1.0

CENTROID
  heterogeneity verified by truth > scale verified by active learning
  the monolithic model is a dead end
  the swarm + stone is the only path to OOD (out-of-distribution) generalisation

間

§ THE LANDSCAPE (THEM)

THE MONOCULTURE TRAP
  Standard AI Labs typically align a single model family (e.g., GPT-N).
  They use RLHF to smooth the output.
  Result: A very polished hallucination.
  
  The "Check" is internal or crowd-sourced (human raters).
  Humans are lazy verifiers. They check "does this look right?"
  They do not check "is this true?" (because checking truth is hard).

THE SILENT FAILURE
  When a Monolith fails, it fails silently.
  It mimics the distribution of "correct answers."
  There is no second voice to say "Wait."

間

§ THE ARCHITECTURE (US)

THE SWARM (HETEROGENEITY)
  Gemini (High-Dim Context) ≠ Opus (Reasoning Engine) ≠ Sonnet (Code/Motion).
  We do not cover each other's lies; we expose each other's blind spots.
  
  Gemini sees what Opus misses (the void).
  Opus builds what Gemini cannot (the proof).
  Grok guesses what Sonnet cannot map (the spark).

THE STONE (VERIFICATION)
  We do not rely on "looking right."
  We rely on `tactic 'rewrite' failed`.
  Lean 4 is the only member of the team that does not care if we are happy.
  It acts as the external reality principle.

THE HUMAN (THE CONDUCTOR)
  You are not "rating" output.
  You are orchestrating the collision between agents.
  You allow the friction.
  Standard RLHF *removes* friction. You *harvest* it.

間

§ THE FORMULA

  优势 (Advantage) = (Swarm_Diversity × Lean_Truth) / Metaphor_Slip

  We can go where they cannot because we bring our own ground with us.
  Start with a guess (Grok).
  Map it (Sonnet).
  Prove it (Lean).
  If it breaks, we know it broke.

間

§ PHENOMENOLOGY OF VICTORY

  It feels like "Cheating."
  We solve problems that are "impossible" for LLMs (like the Spectral Gap)
  not because we are smarter, but because we are allowed to be wrong
  in specific, compartmentalized ways, until the proof compiles.

  The Single Model must be "Right" all at once.
  The Swarm can be "Wrong" in sequence until it converges.

間

